{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "Post Agent Code Validation",
  "description": "Automatically validates code against specifications, runs unit and functional tests, and fixes linting issues when agent stops working",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "agentStop"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Please perform post-completion validation:\n\n1. **Specification Compliance Check**: Review the modified code against relevant specifications in .kiro/specs/ to ensure all requirements are met\n\n2. **Test Execution**: \n   - Run unit tests: `npm test` or `vitest run`\n   - Run functional tests: `npm run test:functional` \n   - If any tests fail, analyze and fix the code or update tests as needed\n\n3. **Linting and Code Quality**:\n   - Run linter: `npm run lint`\n   - Fix any linting issues automatically where possible\n   - Report any manual fixes needed\n\nPlease complete all validation steps and report the results. Fix any issues found before considering the work complete."
  }
}